       LARGEST UNDERFUNDED PENSION LIABILITIES (Dollars)
 --------------------------------------------------------------
Company                  Guaranteed     Assets      Unfunded
                         benefits                  guaranteed
                         liability                  liability
LTV                       3.39 bn       204 m        3.18 bn
American Nat Can           816 m        387 m         429 m
