FT  05 MAR 92 / Observer: Chain reaction
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The super-unions are coming. Yesterday saw an overwhelming vote by members
in favour of amalgamation between the AEU engineering union and the EETPU
electricians union. Public service unions Nupe, Nalgo and Cohse are also
deep in talks.
All that remains is for FTAT, the furniture union, to join forces with MSF
the technical union. Naturally, the new combined union would be refloated
under the name MFI.
