FT  04 MAR 92 / UK Company News: AAF Investment
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
AAF Investment Corporation, 65.5 per cent owned by W&amp;A Investments of South
Africa, continued its development into an industrial holding company in the
1991 year as pre-tax profits improved 11 per cent from Pounds 3.57m to
